Since there were so many it unfortunately took me 2 years to finish reading and analyzing them all. And by then my phone had committed suicide due to the fact that it’s software had to interact with Trumps app.😳😭Is this normal? Because if so, the developers have some real work to do! So in conclusion, I now have to go to a funeral for my phone (#PhoneLivesMatter🥺😭) and cleanse my eyes with bleach because I saw a Trump flag today. TRUMP 2020 but make it Barron🥰🥵🙈🥺
